<head>LOOK DOWN</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">俯視</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>LOOK DOWNWARDS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current general word for looking down is lǎn 覽.</p>
<p>2. Fǔ 俯 refers primarily to facing downwards in order to look down.</p>
